__ Cantrip: Inform ___________________________ Cost: 15 ______________________

Use:  cantrip inform                           Material Component: none
Use:  C inform

The cantrip inform is a minor magic of the spheres of divination.  When 
cast, a field of magic energy fills the room.  The caster will now be 
informed whenever a person enters the field.  The inform cantrip can be
dispelled by entering the room where it was cast and saying < inform off >
